{"tid":2504793,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"護士入行門檻低同辛苦都係講緊某小部分人","createTime":"2021-04-26T06:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T11:34:42.000Z","uid":342891,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6230d85d6ca063b633b3f354843b76163629d47b","tid":2504793,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:52:27.000Z","msg":"讀到書既護士好快就可以唔使輪班唔使做辛苦常規，<br />\n唔使俾人點用自己的護理知識做判斷。<br />\n<br />\n讀唔到書既就冇得選擇要在病房一直輪班一直辛苦，<br />\n連登仔講嚟講去都係講緊呢小部分護士既事，<br />\n根本是兩種護士來。<br />\n只是香港暫時未有分開兩者的法定機制，<br />\n外國是有的。<br />\n<br />\n一個行業的小部分是沒有代表性，<br />\n這是基本邏輯，<br />\n那些葡萄護士的連登仔連基本邏輯都沒有，<br />\n還好意思無理罵人沒邏輯。"},{"pid":"e10ab2bf12b08360d63c630b134c86ced6b0d217","tid":2504793,"uid":43575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"知你叻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59269e4f53f74abbf51f3e08dec0ce718402b782","tid":2504793,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e10ab2bf12b08360d63c630b134c86ced6b0d217","tid":2504793,"uid":43575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"知你叻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:13:23.000Z","msg":"我講緊既係普遍的護士"},{"pid":"1b1059455d6a1aec9073084621a429e43fb9ad2d","tid":2504793,"uid":202022,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e10ab2bf12b08360d63c630b134c86ced6b0d217","tid":2504793,"uid":43575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"知你叻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:14:23.000Z","msg":"佢有少少藍c feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98bbe2ebbbcc826d1ee84b9797f3109e5024599","tid":2504793,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b1059455d6a1aec907